Package: aquametBio
Type: Package
Title: Calculate NRSA and NLA Biological Metrics & Indicators
Version: 2.1.3
Author: Karen Blocksom
Maintainer: Karen Blocksom <blocksom.karen@epa.gov>
Description: This package calculates fish and macroinvertebrate metrics used 
    in the National Rivers and Streams Assessment (NRSA) and the
    National Lakes Assessment (NLA). It also contains functions to assign 
    condition class for fish and macroinvertebrates for NRSA and NLA. Default
    taxa lists as used in NRSA 2013-14 for fish and macroinvertebrates are 
    included in the package.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    Hmisc,
    gtools,
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
